   ENTERTAINMENT (``e'' category)
</P>
<P>
   TV-PREVIEW-DIARY (Undated) _ ``The Secret Diary of Desmond
Pfeiffer'' is one of the most inclusive shows on television. It
will anger everybody. Start with the overall theme, which is
basically the lighter side of slavery. By MARK McGUIRE.
</P>
<P>
   TRAVEL (``t'' category)
</P>
