<HEADER>
A1376 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u v &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ELIMINATE-MAD-COW-CLO     08-25 0048
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ELIMINATE-MAD-COW-CLONES-HNS </SLUG>
  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  
 
Tuesday, Aug. 25, 1998
<TEXT>
<P>
   &QL; 
Editors: &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &QL; 
MAD-COW-CLONES (Undated) _ The MAD-COW-CLONES story will not move
tonight on the Hearst News wire service. &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
<P>
   Houston Chronicle  &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
