covered by the company's decision to reduce stock option exercise
prices? (Waresh, Palm Beach Post) ETA 8 p.m. ET.
</P>
<P>
   BELLSOUTH-PORTABILITY _ ATLANTA _ BellSouth has announced it is
ready to provide ''number portability,'' a key requirement for
giving competititors a chance in local phone service. The idea is
to let customers keep their numbers no matter who their local phone
provider might be. BellSouth needs this to make the case that its
market is open to rivals so it can be permitted into long-distance.
(Kanell, Atlanta Journal-Constitution) ETA 8 p.m. ET.
</P>
<P>
   BELLSOUTH-PAGER _ ATLANTA _ BellSouth introduces a new high-tech
pager than also does e-mail. (Kanell, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
ETA 8 p.m. ET.
