<P>
   TEN-COLLINS-COLUMN (Brookline, Mass.) -- Roy Stanley (Emmo)
Emerson, had made good impressions at Wimbledon, the Australian and
French and US Championships-- almost any place in the world
boasting a tennis court. By Bud Collins.
</P>
<P>
   SOC-REVOLUTION (Foxborough, Mass.) -- Walter Zenga plans to not
only coach the Revolution through the remainder of the MLS season,
but to return as player-coach next season. By Frank Dell'Apa.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; The Boston Globe &LR;  &QC;
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
