perfectly with their pets than with their employers, companies,
eager to attract and retain employees, are allowing employees to
bring pets into work. Ben &AMP; Jerry's Ice Cream has an annual bring
your pet to work day and there is a group trying to have a regular
annual day proclaimed. Therapists say pets at work can relax and
motivate workers and create a more congenial workplace. Some
workers look at their ability to work with their pets as a
prerequisite to accepting a job. PHOTO. By MAX JARMAN. Story moved
in the ``F`` category. &QL; 
