<P>
   ``Anybody who does not abide by the mandatory evacuation, our
law enforcement has been instructed to ask them their next of
kin.''
</P>
<P>
   _GOV. DAVID BEASLEY, of South Carolina, in the path of a
hurricane.
</P>
</TEXT>
